{"tid":1947750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（831 fake news)有問題嘅係Instagram而唔係Boomlive","createTime":"2020-03-28T13:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T15:35:34.000Z","uid":242025,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d33df7bf836107e35fdb554776bd2c7116f2ac0a","tid":1947750,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:20:30.000Z","msg":"其實睇返Boomlive個網，佢係冇話過831事件係fake news，fake嘅係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">印度佬個post將831條片配落武漢肺炎嘅caption到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67rxbxw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67rxbxw.png&h=b551d967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBoomlive個網都有講到明條片係<span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;the video actually shows political protests in Hong Kong in August 2019&rdquo; </span>佢冇講過831事件係fake news。<br />\n<br />\n的確印度佬個post係fake news，831條片同肺炎係無關，Boomlive係冇fact check錯。但問題就係在於Instagram將所有831嘅片都當fake news，即使該post嘅內容同caption係related。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8M5wyc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8M5wyc.png&h=e6b97634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以最大問題係Instagram，亂咁將所有831片當成fake news。我見大家都屌緊間fact check公司，但其實最大問題個個應該係Instagram <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亂咁ban 831條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望大家可以針對返Instagram 而唔係Boomlive。"},{"pid":"36be0c9b96de7900ba394ef25aa7cf213d029aae","tid":1947750,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4b7e43bfe38cc197ef47f0a248c3dc17e0f2ecc","tid":1947750,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:21:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"210da44284764fd720c4688cbf0dcbd86ba1b426","tid":1947750,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7419